{"tid":1545351,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[光復]上水有蝗搞學校，仲話要報晒啲良心老師上教育局2","createTime":"2019-09-06T01:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T09:36:08.000Z","uid":145768,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"58e048b3daf939560c2856b978caf3a3b92bc359","tid":1545351,"uid":145768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:22:25.000Z","msg":"上個POST推唔郁 黎多次<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/368513580020590/posts/1336208506584421?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F368513580020590%2Fposts%2F1336208506584421%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=69520488\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/368513580020590/posts/1336208506584421?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n垃圾hkg報，請先report<br />\n<br />\n事源呢間學校有手足係門口呼籲罷課，奈何蝗卵太多，亦吸引左班自稱蝗母。<br />\n<br />\n呢加班蝗母同籃屍放左間學校上籃屍page，仲揚言要清算老師，報上教育局向老師施壓。<br />\n<br />\n手足，係咪應該幫幫忙，同班蝗母講驚就咪撚出街，最緊要驚班良心老師比人清算。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>係時候要幫班老師手，佢地處於一個被人渣住個春袋既時候</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"43b116f868a4ecc3570366efe0cf893cee9eed0a","tid":1545351,"uid":145768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:22:40.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"a15d0cb27f4c2c11f99155f33e84e5016ef4f4d7","tid":1545351,"uid":145768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:22:50.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"0ef836b19bb3bb9450223f85ecbf62d43adae5e1","tid":1545351,"uid":145768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:23:00.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"ff42a6f02213ced352852520b219557e449c03ab","tid":1545351,"uid":145768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:23:10.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"b90a4757573552596951a3f35b611b4c6599e737","tid":1545351,"uid":145768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:23:25.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"2f8c67c9456